trans-unit.source: Defines methods to dynamically create, update and remove code elements for a type at design time.
trans-unit.target: 定義方法以動態方式建立、 更新和移除在執行階段類型的程式碼項目。

trans-unit.source: Methods are also provided that allow you to display code at design time.
trans-unit.target: 方法也會提供可讓您在設計階段顯示程式碼。

trans-unit.source: Creates an event on the specified class by using the specified event name, event type and attributes.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定的事件名稱、 事件類型和屬性，指定的類別上建立事件。

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the class name to add the event to.
trans-unit.target: 字串，包含要加入至事件的類別名稱。

trans-unit.source: A string that defines the name of the event.
trans-unit.target: 字串，定義事件的名稱。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> assigned to the event.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Type>指派給事件。</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.AttributeInfo"></xref> array that contains information on all attributes to assign to the event.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.AttributeInfo"> </xref>陣列，其中包含要指定給事件的所有屬性的資訊。

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to emit any dependency properties associated with the event; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>若要發出與事件相關聯的任何相依性屬性否則， <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Creates a field on the specified class by using the specified field name, field type, parameter types, attributes and literal initialization expression.
trans-unit.target: 建立指定的類別上的欄位，使用指定的欄位名稱、 欄位類型、 參數類型、 屬性和常值的初始化運算式。

trans-unit.source: A string that defines the name of the class to add the field.
trans-unit.target: 定義要將欄位加入類別名稱的字串。

trans-unit.source: A string that defines the name of the field.
trans-unit.target: 定義的欄位名稱的字串。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> of the new field.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Type>新欄位。</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Type> array of any parameters associated with the field.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Type>欄位相關聯的任何參數的陣列。</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.MemberAttributes"></xref> that defines the member attribute identifier for the field.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.MemberAttributes"> </xref>定義成員屬性識別碼欄位。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetExpression"></xref> that contains the literal expression of the field.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetExpression"> </xref> ，其中包含欄位的常值的運算式。

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to delete any existing fields on `className` when creating the new field; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.

trans-unit.source: Displays code for the new member on a workflow design surface.
trans-unit.target: 顯示工作流程設計介面上的新成員的程式碼。

trans-unit.source: Displays code for the new member on a workflow design surface by using the specified <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref>, the specified method and the specified delegate type.
